  • Field Details

    • INVALID_OBJECT

      static final int INVALID_OBJECT
      Object handle id that can be used to refer to a just created server-side object (for protocol versions supporting ptype_lazy_send).

      This can be used to pipeline the creation of an object with the subsequent use of that object without waiting on the server response with the actual handle id.
